<lb n="0778c13" ed="T"/>羅<note n="0778005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">姿＝婆【明】</note><note n="0778005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">姿【大】，婆【明】</note><app n="0778005"><lem wit="【大】">姿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">婆</rdg></app>馱瞿<note n="0778006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">姿＝婆【三】</note><note n="0778006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">姿【大】，婆【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0778006"><lem wit="【大】">姿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】 【明】">婆</rdg></app><note place="inline">十</note>　阿奴絁失吒<note place="inline">十一</note>　鼻摩帝鉢
